title: MotoGP 2014 Sepang 720p [PT-BR/EN]
description:
First of all, I'd like to apologize for my absence on the last three MotoGP rounds. I couldn't even record one of them due to daytime saving which ended up recording the very ending of last round's race. The other two, I had some personal issues to be accomplished. So I was very busy to upload anything back then.
Either way, that's the Round 17 of 2014 MotoGP Season at Sepang Circuit, in Malaysia, the second-to-last round of the, already defined, championship. On audio track 1, the original brazilian commentaries while on audio track 2, english-Uk commentaries is available.
